<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Variabilidade das Idades à Morte — Resultados do Laboratório</title>
<style>
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=IBM+Plex+Sans:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,600;1,300&family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap');

  :root {
    --bg:       #0f1117;
    --surface:  #181c26;
    --border:   #2a2f3e;
    --swe-dark: #4a90d9;
    --swe-light:#7bbfef;
    --usa-dark: #e05252;
    --usa-light:#f0a0a0;
    --accent:   #f0c040;
    --text:     #e8eaf0;
    --muted:    #8890a8;
    --green:    #5dc887;
    --slide-w:  900px;
  }

  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  body {
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    padding: 2rem 1rem 6rem;
  }

  /* ── Navigation ─────────────────────────────── */
  #nav {
    position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    background: rgba(15,17,23,0.95);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem;
    padding: .6rem 1.5rem; z-index: 100;
    backdrop-filter: blur(6px);
  }
  #nav span { color: var(--muted); font-size: .8rem; flex: 1; }
  .nav-btn {
    background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--text); padding: .3rem .9rem; border-radius: 4px;
    cursor: pointer; font-family: inherit; font-size: .82rem;
    transition: background .15s;
  }
  .nav-btn:hover { background: var(--border); }
  #progress {
    height: 2px; background: var(--accent);
    position: fixed; top: 37px; left: 0;
    transition: width .2s; z-index: 101;
  }

  /* ── Slide container ─────────────────────────── */
  .slide {
    max-width: var(--slide-w);
    margin: 5rem auto 0;
    display: none;
  }
  .slide.active { display: block; }

  /* ── Slide elements ──────────────────────────── */
  .slide-header {
    border-left: 3px solid var(--accent);
    padding-left: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
  }
  .slide-eyebrow {
    font-size: .72rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: .12em;
    text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: .3rem;
  }
  h1 {
    font-size: 1.9rem; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.2;
    color: #fff;
  }
  h2 {
    font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 600; color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .subtitle {
    color: var(--muted); font-size: .9rem; margin-top: .3rem;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  /* ── Cards grid ──────────────────────────────── */
  .grid-2 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1rem; }
  .grid-3 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap: 1rem; }
  .grid-4 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap: .8rem; }

  .card {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1.1rem 1.2rem;
  }
  .card-label {
    font-size: .72rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: .08em;
    text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: .4rem;
  }
  .card-value {
    font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1;
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
  }
  .card-sub { font-size: .78rem; color: var(--muted); margin-top: .3rem; }
  .swe { color: var(--swe-dark); }
  .swe-l { color: var(--swe-light); }
  .usa { color: var(--usa-dark); }
  .usa-l { color: var(--usa-light); }
  .acc { color: var(--accent); }
  .grn { color: var(--green); }

  /* ── Tables ──────────────────────────────────── */
  table {
    width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;
    font-size: .85rem; margin-top: .5rem;
  }
  th {
    background: var(--border); color: var(--muted);
    font-size: .72rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: .06em;
    text-transform: uppercase; padding: .55rem .8rem;
    text-align: left;
  }
  td { padding: .55rem .8rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
  tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
  tr:hover td { background: rgba(255,255,255,.03); }
  .num { font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace; text-align: right; }
  .row-swe1960 td:first-child { border-left: 3px solid var(--swe-dark); }
  .row-swe2019 td:first-child { border-left: 3px solid var(--swe-light); }
  .row-usa1960 td:first-child { border-left: 3px solid var(--usa-dark); }
  .row-usa2019 td:first-child { border-left: 3px solid var(--usa-light); }

  /* ── Interpretation boxes ────────────────────── */
  .interp {
    background: rgba(240,192,64,.07);
    border: 1px solid rgba(240,192,64,.25);
    border-radius: 6px; padding: 1rem 1.2rem;
    margin-top: 1rem; font-size: .88rem;
  }
  .interp-title {
    font-weight: 600; color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: .4rem; font-size: .8rem;
    text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .06em;
  }
  .interp p { margin-bottom: .4rem; color: var(--text); }
  .interp p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

  /* ── Bar charts (CSS) ────────────────────────── */
  .bar-row {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: .8rem;
    margin-bottom: .55rem;
  }
  .bar-label { width: 90px; font-size: .8rem; color: var(--muted); flex-shrink: 0; }
  .bar-track {
    flex: 1; height: 22px; background: var(--border);
    border-radius: 3px; overflow: hidden; position: relative;
  }
  .bar-fill {
    height: 100%; border-radius: 3px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; padding-left: .4rem;
    font-size: .72rem; font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    color: #fff; font-weight: 500; transition: width .6s ease;
  }
  .bar-extra { font-size: .78rem; font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
               color: var(--muted); flex-shrink: 0; width: 60px; text-align: right; }

  /* ── Lorenz-like diagram (SVG inline) ───────── */
  .svg-wrap { background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border);
              border-radius: 8px; padding: 1rem; }

  /* ── Split stacked bar (Theil decomp) ────────── */
  .decomp-bar {
    height: 32px; border-radius: 4px; overflow: hidden;
    display: flex; margin-bottom: .5rem;
  }
  .decomp-seg {
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: .78rem; font-weight: 600;
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace; color: #fff;
    transition: width .5s ease;
  }

  /* ── Footnote ────────────────────────────────── */
  .footnote {
    margin-top: 1.5rem; font-size: .75rem; color: var(--muted);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border); padding-top: .7rem;
  }

  /* ── Slide counter ───────────────────────────── */
  #counter { font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace; font-size: .8rem; color: var(--muted); }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- Navigation -->
<div id="nav">
  <button class="nav-btn" onclick="go(-1)">← Anterior</button>
  <span id="slide-title">—</span>
  <span id="counter">1 / 12</span>
  <button class="nav-btn" onclick="go(1)">Próximo →</button>
</div>
<div id="progress"></div>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════════
     SLIDE 1 — Título
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<div class="slide active" id="s1" data-title="Apresentação">
  <div style="min-height:420px; display:flex; flex-direction:column; justify-content:center;">
    <div style="margin-bottom:2rem;">
      <div class="slide-eyebrow">Doutorado em Demografia · CEDEPLAR/UFMG</div>
      <h1 style="font-size:2.4rem; margin:.5rem 0;">Variabilidade das<br>Idades à Morte</h1>
      <div class="subtitle" style="font-size:1rem; margin-top:.6rem;">
        Resultados do Laboratório · Suécia e EUA, mulheres, 1960 e 2019
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="grid-4">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-label">Tópico 1</div>
        <div style="font-size:.9rem; font-weight:600; color:var(--text)">Idade Modal</div>
        <div class="card-sub">5 métodos de estimação</div>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-label">Tópico 2</div>
        <div style="font-size:.9rem; font-weight:600; color:var(--text)">e†, H, Gini</div>
        <div class="card-sub">Medidas de variabilidade</div>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-label">Tópico 3</div>
        <div style="font-size:.9rem; font-weight:600; color:var(--text)">Threshold age</div>
        <div class="card-sub">a† de Zhang & Vaupel</div>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-label">Tópico 4</div>
        <div style="font-size:.9rem; font-weight:600; color:var(--text)">Theil</div>
        <div class="card-sub">Decomposição entre/dentro</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footnote">
      Dados: Human Mortality Database (mortality.org) · Pacote LifeIneq (van Raalte & Riffe)
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════════
     SLIDE 2 — e0, Mediana e Moda
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<div class="slide" id="s2" data-title="e₀, Mediana e Moda">
  <div class="slide-header">
    <div class="slide-eyebrow">Medidas de Localização</div>
    <h1>e₀, Mediana e Moda (M)</h1>
    <div class="subtitle">A moda é sempre maior que a mediana e e₀ em populações modernas</div>
  </div>
  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>População</th>
        <th class="num">e₀</th>
        <th class="num">Mediana</th>
        <th class="num">Moda M<br><span style="font-weight:400;font-style:italic">(spline, ≥40)</span></th>
        <th class="num">Gap M − e₀</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr class="row-swe1960">
        <td><span class="swe">●</span> SWE 1960</td>
        <td class="num">74.9</td><td class="num">74.4</td>
        <td class="num">81.2</td>
        <td class="num acc">+6.3</td>
      </tr>
      <tr class="row-swe2019">
        <td><span class="swe-l">●</span> SWE 2019</td>
        <td class="num">84.7</td><td class="num">84.5</td>
        <td class="num">90.0</td>
        <td class="num acc">+5.3</td>
      </tr>
      <tr class="row-usa1960">
        <td><span class="usa">●</span> USA 1960</td>
        <td class="num">73.3</td><td class="num">73.1</td>
        <td class="num">79.9</td>
        <td class="num acc">+6.6</td>
      </tr>
      <tr class="row-usa2019">
        <td><span class="usa-l">●</span> USA 2019</td>
        <td class="num">81.5</td><td class="num">81.3</td>
        <td class="num">89.1</td>
        <td class="num acc">+7.6</td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
  <div class="interp">
    <div class="interp-title">Interpretação</div>
    <p><strong>e₀ ≈ Mediana</strong> em todas as populações — a distribuição de mortes é aproximadamente simétrica em torno da expectativa de vida.</p>
    <p><strong>M sempre supera e₀ em 5–8 anos</strong> porque d(x) tem assimetria à esquerda: pouquíssimas mortes prematuras puxam e₀ levemente para baixo, mas não deslocam o pico da distribuição.</p>
    <p><strong>Gap maior nos EUA 2019 (+7.6 anos)</strong> reflete maior dispersão da distribuição de mortes — mortalidade menos comprimida que na Suécia.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="footnote">Moda estimada por spline cúbico, recorte ≥ 40 anos (Canudas-Romo, 2010). Dados: HMD, mulheres.</div>
</div>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════════
     SLIDE 3 — Cinco métodos para a moda
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<div class="slide" id="s3" data-title="Cinco métodos para a moda">
  <div class="slide-header">
    <div class="slide-eyebrow">Estimação da Idade Modal</div>
    <h1>Comparação de 5 Métodos (recorte ≥ 40)</h1>
    <div class="subtitle">Desvio em relação ao Spline cúbico como referência</div>
  </div>
  <div class="grid-2" style="gap:1.2rem;">
    <div>
      <h2 style="font-size:1rem; color:var(--muted); margin-bottom:.8rem;">Estimativas (anos)</h2>
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr><th>Método</th><th class="num">SWE 60</th><th class="num">SWE 19</th><th class="num">USA 60</th><th class="num">USA 19</th></tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td>Discreto</td><td class="num">81</td><td class="num">90</td><td class="num">80</td><td class="num">89</td></tr>
          <tr><td style="color:var(--accent); font-weight:600;">Spline ★</td><td class="num acc">81.2</td><td class="num acc">90.0</td><td class="num acc">79.9</td><td class="num acc">89.1</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Gompertz</td><td class="num">81.4</td><td class="num">90.3</td><td class="num">81.4</td><td class="num">88.6</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Kernel bw=5</td><td class="num">80.1</td><td class="num">88.9</td><td class="num">80.9</td><td class="num">88.0</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Máx f(x)</td><td class="num">81.6</td><td class="num">90.5</td><td class="num">80.4</td><td class="num">89.6</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h2 style="font-size:1rem; color:var(--muted); margin-bottom:.8rem;">Desvio médio absoluto vs. Spline</h2>
      <div class="bar-row">
        <div class="bar-label">Discreto</div>
        <div class="bar-track">
          <div class="bar-fill" style="width:7%; background:#5dc887;">0.10</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bar-extra">menor ✓</div>
      </div>
      <div class="bar-row">
        <div class="bar-label">Gompertz</div>
        <div class="bar-track">
          <div class="bar-fill" style="width:46%; background:#f0c040;">0.62</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bar-extra">superestima</div>
      </div>
      <div class="bar-row">
        <div class="bar-label">Máx f(x)</div>
        <div class="bar-track">
          <div class="bar-fill" style="width:35%; background:#f0c040;">0.47</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bar-extra">+0.5 sist.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="bar-row">
        <div class="bar-label">Kernel bw=5</div>
        <div class="bar-track">
          <div class="bar-fill" style="width:80%; background:#e05252;">1.07</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bar-extra">maior ✗</div>
      </div>
      <div class="interp" style="margin-top:.8rem;">
        <div class="interp-title">Por que o Kernel diverge?</div>
        <p>bw=5 suaviza demais o pico estreito de SWE 2019 (M≈90), deslocando o máximo para a esquerda. Use bw=2–3 para populações modernas.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="footnote">★ Spline cúbico como referência (Horiuchi et al., 2013; Kannisto, 2001).</div>
</div>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════════
     SLIDE 4 — Recorte etário e bimodalidade histórica
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<div class="slide" id="s4" data-title="Recorte etário e bimodalidade">
  <div class="slide-header">
    <div class="slide-eyebrow">Por que o recorte em 40 anos existe</div>
    <h1>Bimodalidade Histórica — Sweden females</h1>
    <div class="subtitle">O recorte é um critério de identificação, não de sensibilidade</div>
  </div>
  <div class="grid-2">
    <div>
      <h2 style="font-size:1rem;">Moda com e sem recorte</h2>
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr><th>Ano</th><th class="num">e₀</th><th class="num">Moda (≥0)</th><th class="num">Moda (≥40)</th><th>Bimodal?</th></tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td>SWE 1800</td><td class="num">33.1</td>
            <td class="num usa">0</td>
            <td class="num grn">71.8</td>
            <td><span class="usa">SIM ←</span></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>SWE 1900</td><td class="num">53.5</td>
            <td class="num usa">0</td>
            <td class="num grn">78.2</td>
            <td><span class="usa">SIM ←</span></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>SWE 1950</td><td class="num">72.4</td>
            <td class="num grn">80</td>
            <td class="num grn">80</td>
            <td><span class="grn">não</span></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>SWE 1960</td><td class="num">74.9</td>
            <td class="num grn">81.2</td>
            <td class="num grn">81.2</td>
            <td><span class="grn">não</span></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>SWE 2019</td><td class="num">84.7</td>
            <td class="num grn">90.0</td>
            <td class="num grn">90.0</td>
            <td><span class="grn">não</span></td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
    <div>
      <!-- Schematic d(x) bimodal -->
      <div class="svg-wrap">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 340 180" style="width:100%;display:block;">
          <text x="170" y="14" text-anchor="middle" fill="#8890a8" font-size="10" font-family="IBM Plex Sans">d(x) esquemático — SWE 1800</text>
          <!-- axes -->
          <line x1="30" y1="160" x2="320" y2="160" stroke="#2a2f3e" stroke-width="1.5"/>
          <line x1="30" y1="20"  x2="30"  y2="160" stroke="#2a2f3e" stroke-width="1.5"/>
          <!-- infant peak -->
          <rect x="32" y="45" width="18" height="115" fill="#e05252" opacity=".7" rx="2"/>
          <text x="41" y="40" text-anchor="middle" fill="#e05252" font-size="9">pico infantil</text>
          <!-- senile hump -->
          <ellipse cx="220" cy="110" rx="55" ry="50" fill="#4a90d9" opacity=".35"/>
          <line x1="220" y1="60" x2="220" y2="160" stroke="#4a90d9" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-dasharray="4,3"/>
          <text x="220" y="55" text-anchor="middle" fill="#4a90d9" font-size="9">pico senil</text>
          <!-- cutoff line -->
          <line x1="115" y1="20" x2="115" y2="160" stroke="#f0c040" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-dasharray="5,3"/>
          <text x="118" y="30" fill="#f0c040" font-size="9">recorte 40a</text>
          <!-- x labels -->
          <text x="30"  y="172" text-anchor="middle" fill="#8890a8" font-size="9">0</text>
          <text x="115" y="172" text-anchor="middle" fill="#8890a8" font-size="9">40</text>
          <text x="220" y="172" text-anchor="middle" fill="#8890a8" font-size="9">70</text>
          <text x="310" y="172" text-anchor="middle" fill="#8890a8" font-size="9">110</text>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="interp" style="margin-top:.8rem;">
        <div class="interp-title">Lição</div>
        <p>Em 1800 e 1900, <code>argmax(dx)</code> sem recorte retorna idade 0 (pico infantil). O recorte ≥40 força o algoritmo a buscar o pico senil. Em populações modernas os dois convergem — o recorte é redundante mas inofensivo.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="footnote">Canudas-Romo (2010), Demographic Research 22. Dados: HMD, Sweden females.</div>
</div>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════════
